title: The.Face.UK.S01E08.Final.WEB-DLx264.JIVE.mp4
description: To find the perfect fit for the cosmetics brand the contestants are competing to become the face of, the judges ask the hopefuls to pose for beauty shots and star in an online advert. The weakest performer is immediately sent home empty handed before the three remaining contenders strut down the catwalk at London's One Mayfair in a final chance to impress. After eight weeks of challenges, the winner is revealed.
